 prompt\n\nAdjust **Guider**, **Sampler**, **Scheduler**\n\nIf You **don't** want to upscale the **Image**, use the **Set Mode** nodes to **bypass** both **Upscale Image (using Model)** and **Upscale Image** nodes.\n\nIf Your **Upscale Model** is let's say **4x** but You only want **2x**, You can Resize **after** Upscaling: Make sure **both** Upscale Image (using Model) and Upscale Image nodes set to **Enabled**. Set the **Resolution Calulator**'s **Multiplier** to **2** which will take the **Input Image Dimensions**, multiplies it by **2** and passes it to the Upscale Image **Width** and **Height** parammeters.\n\nFinally, set the self-explanatory parameters of the **Tiled Sampler** and **run** the **Workflow**.\n\n---\n\n## Important!\n\nDo **NOT** use **Mute** on Upscaler / Resizer! Enable or Bypass only.\n\n---\n\nThe **Multiplier** is applied to the **original** Input Image dimensions. With **Multiplier** set to **2**, You'll double the original image size regardless of what Upscale Model You're using if Resizer is enabled. When the Resizer is Bypassed, the Multiplier does nothing.\n\n---\n\n## Dependency\n\nThis workflow uses **RMBG** to remove background, and since **RMBG**'s segmenter is **broken** (for me at least), **SAM3** is also required. Install those first. Alternatively, You can create and use Your own Mask(s).\n\n---\n\n## Color Codes\n\n### Red Nodes\n\nNormally **Loaders** and things You **need** to change for Your specific setup **before** First Use\n\n---\n\n### Purple Nodes\n\nThings You probably **will** interact with the most\n\n---\n\n### Blue Nodes\n\nGenerally just **stet it and forget it** nodes that You'll set once\n\n---\n\n### Black Nodes\nYou don't ever really need to touch those\n"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":12,"type":"RandomNoise","pos":[1390,30],"size":[300,82],"flags":{"collapsed":false},"order":4,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"Seed","localized_name":"noise_seed","name":"noise_seed","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"noise_seed"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"NOISE","name":"NOISE","type":"NOISE","links":[24]}],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"RandomNoise"},"widgets_values":[551239030604573,"randomize"],"color":"#323","bgcolor":"#535"}],"links":[[3,1,0,4,0,"MODEL"],[4,1,1,4,1,"CLIP"],[5,2,0,6,0,"IMAGE"],[6,4,1,7,0,"CLIP"],[7,5,0,8,0,"UPSCALE_MODEL"],[8,6,0,8,1,"IMAGE"],[9,8,0,9,0,"IMAGE"],[10,6,1,9,2,"INT"],[11,6,2,9,3,"INT"],[12,9,0,11,0,"IMAGE"],[13,4,0,13,0,"MODEL"],[14,7,0,13,1,"CONDITIONING"],[15,7,1,13,2,"CONDITIONING"],[16,4,0,15,0,"MODEL"],[17,9,0,16,0,"IMAGE"],[18,1,2,16,1,"VAE"],[19,10,0,17,0,"SAM3_MODEL"],[20,11,0,17,1,"IMAGE"],[21,10,0,18,0,"SAM3_MODEL"],[22,11,0,18,1,"IMAGE"],[24,12,0,20,0,"NOISE"],[25,13,0,20,1,"GUIDER"],[26,14,0,20,2,"SAMPLER"],[27,15,0,20,3,"SIGMAS"],[28,20,0,22,0,"LATENT"],[29,1,2,22,1,"VAE"],[30,22,0,24,0,"IMAGE"],[31,6,0,24,1,"IMAGE"],[40,8,0,3,0,"IMAGE"],[41,9,0,3,1,"IMAGE"],[42,17,1,3,2,"IMAGE"],[43,18,1,3,3,"IMAGE"],[47,17,0,19,0,"MASK"],[48,18,0,19,1,"MASK"],[49,9,0,19,3,"IMAGE"],[50,16,0,19,4,"LATENT"],[51,19,0,20,4,"LATENT"],[52,19,1,21,0,"MASK"],[53,19,2,23,0,"IMAGE"]],"groups":[],"config":{},"extra":{"workflowRendererVersion":"LG","ds":{"scale":0.5669106881405565,"offset":[569.7146579080375,595.2925074259439]}},"version":0.4}